
	##ver-0.0_3## - Important Update

	News:

	1- Added make install, uninstall and clean command.
	2- Added version checker.
	3- Added menu for selecting calculation or version checking.
	4- + Minor updates (fix, etc...)

	Goals for ver-0.0_4:

	1- Adding more than two number calculating option.
	2- Adding new calculation types.
	3- Adding recalculation mechanism.

	Goals for ver-0.1 - Big Update:

	1- Adding mini GUI (opencalc pack will be doesn't include this feature
	   for extra performance. GUI option will be added downloadable option.)
	2- Removing option numbers (new selection mechanism).
	3- New ideas will be added in other versions.


